api

Interface IndexedNeighborGraph<S>

  • Type Parameters:
    S - The vertex type on which the graph structure is defined.
    All Superinterfaces:
    NeighborGraph<S>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IndexedColorGraph<S,C>, IndexedNavigableRootedNeighborGraph<S>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BreadthFirstNeighborGraphBuilder, IndexedColorGraphBase, IndexedColorGraphBuilder, IndexedNavigableRootedNeighborGraphBase, IndexedNeighborGraphBase, IndexedNeighborGraphBuilder

    public interface IndexedNeighborGraph<S>
extends NeighborGraph<S>
    Extension of the NeighborGraph API for graphs whose vertices are indexed by the the natural numbers 1, 2, ..., getNumberOfVertices().
    Author:
    pdokos
